/* -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

  CRTICEPGM STMF('/www/IceBreak-Samples/msXlate.rpgle') SVRID(samples)


  By     Date       PTF     Description
  ------ ---------- ------- ---------------------------------------------------
  NLI    22.06.2019         New program
